transcript:
Customer: Hello
Executive: Hello
Customer: Haan ji sir bataye.
Executive: Haan ji sir good morning.
Customer: Good morning, bataiye.
Executive: Bol raha hu hai kya online.
Executive: Haan ji.
Customer: Haan haan. Mai online hu koi dikkat. Haan haan.
Executive: Ek minute.

Executive: Sir link bheja join karenge toh aapko whatsapp pe kiya hai.
Customer: Ji.


Executive: Kariye rahe sir.
Customer: Hello.
Executive: Laptop pe thoda aawaz ja rahi hai sir.
Customer: Mai connect matlab mai connect kar chuka hu apne side se aap accept daliye na.
Executive: Ji.
Customer: Aawaz ja rahi hai kya meri laptop ke side se?
Executive: Haan toh voice call cut karu?
Customer: Haan matlab aawaz ja rahi hai na meri?
Executive: Haan aa rahi hai mujhe.
Customer: Ek minute. Aapka side mute pe hai.
Customer: Nahi toh call cut karna padega na phir mujhe.
Executive: Wait. Hello.
Executive: Hello.
Customer: Hello.
Executive: Sir aap mute pe ho shayad ek baar aap boliyega toh whatsapp ke through. Sorry laptop ke through.
Customer: Laptop ke through connect kar raha hu ek minute ruko.

Customer: Hello.
Executive: Haan ji sir abhi aawaz aa rahi hai. Theek hai mai phone
